data.description: Big price reduction! Welcome to this upgraded home in the 55+ community of Warm Spring Knolls in Murrieta. This is a manufactured home, but you own the land! It’s a spacious 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom plus bonus room with an open floor plan. The kitchen features a newer dishwasher, microwave oven and a 5 burner stove with center griddle and convection oven! Comes with a French drawer refrigerator/freezer with door ice and water. Both bathrooms have been tastefully remodeled with the latest finishes, with sparkling raised glass sinks offering a modern and stylish living space. Master bath features a jetted soaking tub and lighted vanity mirror with a walk-in linen closet and the second bath features a no step walk-in shower. There are ceiling fans in all bedrooms, living room and patio and mirrored closets in all bedrooms. Keep your clothes and shoes organized with beautiful Closet World Custom Closets in the bedrooms. The third bedroom is versatile and can be used as a true bedroom or a convenient office space. Ample storage is available throughout the home, including an extra hobby room off the back. Enjoy the cozy ambiance of the gas and wood burning fireplace with tile surround and the energy efficiency of double-pane windows. This home features a one-car garage with tons of storage and an automatic garage door opener. There’s a large outside storage shed with electrical. Additional amenities include a newer HVAC system, Nest thermostat, Ring doorbell with a flat screen wall mount in the living room. The home is surrounded by a lovely patio garden with an awning providing a relaxing outdoor space. The community center has a pool and Jacuzzi and hosts lots of events. Conveniently located near shopping and major freeways, this property offers both comfort and accessibility. Don't miss the opportunity to make this charming house your home.
